{
  "description": "A close-up photograph showcases the interior of a vibrant purple tulip. The petals are a rich, deep shade of purple, creating a sense of depth and texture. Visible within the flower are the stamens and pistil, the pistil being a pale yellow-green and the stamens dark brown. The petals curve gently inward, forming a delicate cup shape. The background is a dark, almost black void, which emphasizes the flower and its colors. The lighting highlights the texture of the petals, creating shadows and accentuating their soft, velvety appearance.",
